oc:kn_11286686 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When defining the Entity Disambiguation section" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Include entity disambiguation for ambiguous terms (e.g., 'User' could mean Account, Organization, etc.) and document join keys between entities." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Ambiguous entity references are the most common source of incorrect joins and miscounted metrics in multi-tenant systems." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_a304fbb5 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:OutputFormat ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When assembling the final generated skill document" ;
    oc:directiveContent "The generated skill must include: frontmatter (name, description), SQL dialect section, entity disambiguation, business terminology table, standard filters, key metrics with formulas, data freshness table, knowledge base navigation, common query patterns, and troubleshooting." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Each section serves a distinct purpose in helping an agent write correct, performant queries for the specific company's data warehouse." .

oc:kn_e206f327 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating a new data analysis skill from this template" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never leave [PLACEHOLDER] text in the generated skill — every placeholder must be replaced with actual values from the discovered data context." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Unfilled placeholders produce a non-functional skill that will mislead the agent with generic or missing information." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_eb086ff1 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When customizing the template for a specific company" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Prefer specific column names, table names, and real example queries over generic advice. Remove sections that don't apply to the target company." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Specificity is the primary value driver — generic data advice provides no advantage over baseline SQL knowledge." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_fdd13046 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When defining the Standard Filters section" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Standard filters (test/internal/fraud exclusions) must always be included in the generated skill and explicitly documented with override conditions." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Missing standard filters lead to inflated metrics and incorrect analysis results that include test or invalid data." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

